768
00:45:17.536 --> 00:45:21.436
We expressed acyl carrier protein with a FLAG-tag.

769
00:45:21.496 --> 00:45:24.856
We purified it and used a similar endopeptidase,

770
00:45:25.016 --> 00:45:28.876
Aspen, in order to release this acyl chains

771
00:45:28.885 --> 00:45:32.516
from ACP. And this was a really cool result

772
00:45:32.696 --> 00:45:36.606
