785
00:46:18.496 --> 00:46:21.986
acid biosynthesis and various chains in this pathway.

786
00:46:23.396 --> 00:46:27.326
And while this work was primarily through biochemistry, it was

787
00:46:27.356 --> 00:46:31.176
very gratifying to see other data sets, and in this case, the

